name: IngredientManufacturerRole
title: Ingredient Manufacturer Role
description: Cross-version difference of The way in which this manufacturer is associated with the ingredient. For example whether it is a possible one (others allowed), or an exclusive authorized one for this ingredient. Note that this is not the manufacturing process role.
